Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maniac!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Why? Why won't\Nanyone believe me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming and they're\Ngonna level this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] They'll think I'm\Nlying if I try to warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my home and\NI love everyone in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you wanna\Nlittle help or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, fine, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be?!\NThey're Captain Kuro's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think we'd\Nrisk our lives out of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] "Clash with\Nthe Black Cat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Battle on the Slope!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At daybreak, the pirates\Nwill be landing at this shore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin their attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only way that they'll\Nbe able to get to the village
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is to go up this slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the shoreline\Nis sheer cliffs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so they have to\Ncome through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can fight them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,while they're funneled\Ninto that narrow pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,their numbers\Nwon't mean anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the village\Nwill be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, sounds pretty easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Talking about it is, but\Nvictory depends on our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you guys can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this time\Nyou'd better fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just making a funny.\NC'mon, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NAh, Klahadore. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NHow is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] She's resting just now.\NShe was quite exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] I leave town for a few\Nhours to tend to some errands,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything falls to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That Usopp certainly knows how\Nto cause trouble, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of everything\Nelse he's done today,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he claimed you were a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I can't think of\Na more outrageous lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a\Npresent of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From Miss Kaya\Nto you, Klahadore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three years since\Nyou came to this mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and this gift is to say\Nthank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a commemoration of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The glasses you're wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are always slipping and you\Nhave to push them back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the lady of the house custom\Nordered a new pair for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just the most\Nthoughtful young woman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you've ever met?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be a day\Nworth commemorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NIt's a crescent moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] It's on nights like\Nthese that I truly feel alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart races, and my\Nblood boils in my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do such a thing\Nto Miss Kaya's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll be receiving\Na gift all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be her entire estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NWhat're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose there's no reason\Nto carry on the act any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the village will be mourning\Nthe unforeseen tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Three long years I've\Nquietly waited for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] Miss! You have\Nto get out of here! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NCaptain Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Jango, it's almost\Ndaybreak, it's time get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NGood morning, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NGood morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the sun can wake me up\Nand live to tell about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in a really bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornings are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NJust look,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the moon is still up, so the\Nsun couldn't have woken me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, which one of you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES] Our apologies, sir!\NWe're very sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWell, in that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NWait, what's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He was mad just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? He's in a\Nbetter mood now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's all that matters\Nso keep your big trap shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NIt's confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE E] Oh yeah, well,\Nyour face is confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE D]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I'm a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'll be able\Nto make it up this slope now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All this oil we put here\Nshould keep them occupied
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,while we go to work on 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna be busy\Nslipping and sliding around
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,like a bunch of idiots,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then we show up and beat\Nthe crap out of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, so that's your plan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to defend the village\Nno matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Let's just hope none\Nof us slip on that oil
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and end up down there with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that would be like\Nsliding into a meat grinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp, I gotta hand it to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're pretty good\Nat fighting dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone alive who\Ncan best me with a sling shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or beat me at the art\Nof fighting dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NIt's almost daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A]\NWe're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] All right, men!\NYou know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ashore! Trash the village!\NHead for the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NAye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F] Captain, there are\Nalready two boats here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NShall I investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NLeave 'em for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look like\Ntreasure ships to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have a schedule to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you waiting for?!\NIt's time to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's up. What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Huh...\NMaybe they over slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna show up all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm hearing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it sounds like battle\Ncries from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I definitely hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What can't be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shore just\Nlike this to the north!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They went...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the wrong\Nshore?! That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Well, this is where\Nthey had their secret meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just assumed okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they make it to\Nthe village! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to head\Ndirectly north from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you run you, could\Nmake it in three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrain there is\Nalmost exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so all we need to do\Nis stop them at the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry,\Nwe're gonna stop 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If those filthy pirates\Nare at the north shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then they've already\Nseen our boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there in 20 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My brilliant oil strategy\Nwas all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?\NLet's get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! I'm gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but you understand,\Nthe treasure's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That oil won't be a\Nproblem for you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear on my life, they'll\Nnever set foot in my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That Luffy sure is\Na good runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so far ahead, I can't\Neven see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Run straight north!\NRun straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Run straight north!\NRun straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those mongrels\Nare in big trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if they so much as\Nlook at my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ambush!\NSomebody's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I am the legendary\NCaptain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All my men and I are ready\Nto fight to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn back now if you\Nvalue your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I wasn't supposed\Nto be the first one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He was running way ahead of me.\NI can't handle these guys alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NCrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed\Nto get past this stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] The village...\NThat can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He said run north and I ran\Nin a cold-ish direction
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I should be at the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the troublesome\Nbrats who overheard our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave here while you still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,\Nmy 100 million crewmen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,will massacre all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really supposed\Nto believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! 100 million! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I]\NCaptain! He's obviously lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J] Then it's time\Nto call his bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThey saw through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE K] That guy seriously\Nthought he could fool us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! You've been\Nlying to us this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE L] Captain Jango,\Ntake a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE L]\NNo, sir! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We searched those other ships
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and found a huge\Nload of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say how much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but I bet it's around\Nfive million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Five million berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did those guys\Nget ahold of so much treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI see you found my loot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE K] You're just gonna\Nlet us take your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NThat's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turn around and\Nforget all about this place
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the treasure is yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think people that\Nstupid actually existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, he's just\Nembarrassing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, do you know\Nwhat a pirate is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to\Ntake this treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing\Nyou can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is no way\Nwe're turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,until we get what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NAll righ, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On the count of "one, two,\NJango," you'll let us by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] It's that strange\Nweapon from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO]\NOne, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever try to give\Nmy-hard earned treasure away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey! Who is this crazy girl?!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be\Nhypnotizing yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we got a mission to\Ncarry out, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat treasure boat is mine
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not gonna let\Nyou have a single berry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya hear me? In fact\Nyou better clear out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause I'm coming down\Nthere to get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That really hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Who said you could\Ngive them my treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You got what you deserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI didn't give them the treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said I would\Ngive it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I forgot to\Nmention it to ya earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,don't ever watch\Nhis ring routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That weirdo's a hypnotist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnotist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fast runner, I thought\Nhe'd be here way ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. He either got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or he chickened out\Nat the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighss] The only thing that\Ncould keep him from a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right when we need him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I'll go ahead\Nand take command here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time\Nyou go 'n kick their butts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] What?! Me?!\NWhat about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take on a boatload\Nof vicious pirates by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Like I'm gonna\Ndo any fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath this calm exterior lies\Nthe abject terror of a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you think you're scared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm so scared I am\Nliterally about to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Please! Your eyes\Nare completely dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to do\Nbetter than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Liars can smell their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's just your upper lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI got beat up by...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] We don't have\Ntime for this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, men,\Nlet's get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush them and\Nmove to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--[PIRATES yelling]\N--[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I know!\NI have some caltrops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just what\Nthe doctor ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gonna love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Caltrop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...if your still alive\Nwhen I get outta here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NTake that, oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... how do I get to\Nthe north shore from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Run straight north!\NRun straight north!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Run straight nor--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But which way is north?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! We got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out! Here comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go! You're quite\Nthe warrior after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got this handled\Nso I'll just take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't\Ndone anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are caltrops behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You dropped those\Nthings behind us, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. Don't tell me\Nyou really thought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you were going to\Nstop us down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, fellas!\NCaptain Kuro hates waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M]\NYou again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you jackass!\NYou want some more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Have some!\NHave a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...let you step foot\Nin that village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was lie\Nlike I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Today will be like every other\Nday in that sleepy little town,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause you and your cronies\Nwill never set foot in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE O]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE I]\NStupid girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI yelps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans] Treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NAre you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I won't\Ntell you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[JANGO] We've wasted enough\Ntime playing pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bothering with them\Nand move to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or have you forgotten that this\Nis Captain Kuro's operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he doesn't look favorably\Non his well laid plans
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,being ruined by idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll kill us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand that,\Nyou cretins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's get to the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NDon't go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn back. Don't take\Nanother step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE F]\NGet off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPlease, don't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave this village alone.\NThey're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't deserve this.\NI love this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE G]\NWhat is this, Captain Jango?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE M] Nobody told us\Nthat killers like those
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,were gonna be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the best those\Npirates can dish out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was hopin'\Nfor a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After leaving me down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you're lucky I'm not\Nkickin' your butt too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ussop, you big bonehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me which\Ndirection was north!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO]\NThey're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't appreciate\Ntardiness. Not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They know full well\Nwhat happens to those
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,who are foolish enough\Nto upset my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Do they think they\Ncan take their sweet time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if they have\Nforgotten the consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of disappointing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the butler\Nfrom Kaya's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so early\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he walking to the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:24:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.65,0:24:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.70,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.92,0:24:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NIs this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.45,0:24:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'm gonna get you, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you leave\Nme down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.83,0:24:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NCrap! Zoro's really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.79,0:24:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNow your gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.05,0:24:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the count of\N"one, two, Jango,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll fall deeply asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.10,0:24:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] You wish!\NHey, Luffy! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.18,0:24:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NOh, look at that guy's hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.52,0:24:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NDon't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.99,0:24:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Terrifying Duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.41,0:24:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Meowban Brothers vs. Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

